{"word":"H3173 - יָחִיד - yâchîyd - yaw-kheed' - Darling","slug":"H3173","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָחִיד</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâchîyd"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-kheed'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Darling"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05D7;&#x05D9;&#x05D3; - ya&#x0302;ch&#x0131;&#x0302;yd</b> - <i>yaw-kheed'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3161\">H3161</a>; properly <i>united</i>, that is, <i>sole</i>; by implication <i>beloved</i>; also <i>lonely</i>; (feminine) the <i>life</i> (as not to be replace): - darling, desolate, only (child, son), solitary."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3161\">H3161</a>, <a href=\"#/H3162\">H3162</a>, <a href=\"#/H3163\">H3163</a>, <a href=\"#/H3170\">H3170</a>"}]}